#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.173"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.173:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.173:0.2"
msgid "17. Jāṇussoṇivagga "
msgstr "17. With Jāṇussoṇi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.173:0.3"
msgid "173. Tatiyaadhammasutta "
msgstr "173. Bad Principles (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.173:1.1"
msgid "“Adhammo ca, bhikkhave, veditabbo dhammo ca; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should know bad principles and good principles. "

msgctxt "an10.173:1.2"
msgid "anattho ca veditabbo attho ca. "
msgstr "And you should know bad results and good results. "

msgctxt "an10.173:1.3"
msgid "Adhammañca viditvā dhammañca, anatthañca viditvā atthañca yathā dhammo yathā attho tathā paṭipajjitabbaṃ. "
msgstr "Knowing these things, your practice should follow the good principles with good results. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.173:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, adhammo, katamo ca dhammo; "
msgstr "So what are bad principles? What are good principles? What are bad results? And what are good results? "

msgctxt "an10.173:2.2"
msgid "katamo ca anattho, katamo ca attho? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.173:2.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipāto, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Killing living creatures is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:2.4"
msgid "pāṇātipātā veramaṇī dhammo; "
msgstr "Not killing living creatures is a good principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:2.5"
msgid "ye ca pāṇātipātapaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti, ayaṃ anattho; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by killing living creatures are bad results. "

msgctxt "an10.173:2.6"
msgid "pāṇātipātā veramaṇipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, ayaṃ attho. "
msgstr "And the many skillful qualities fully developed because of not killing living creatures are good results. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.261, sc3
msgctxt "an10.173:3.1"
msgid "Adinnādānaṃ, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Stealing is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.2"
msgid "adinnādānā veramaṇī dhammo … "
msgstr "Not stealing is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.3"
msgid "kāmesumicchācāro, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Sexual misconduct is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.4"
msgid "kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇī dhammo … "
msgstr "Avoiding sexual misconduct is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.5"
msgid "musāvādo, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Lying is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.6"
msgid "musāvādā veramaṇī dhammo … "
msgstr "Not lying is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.7"
msgid "pisuṇā vācā, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Divisive speech is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.8"
msgid "pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇī dhammo … "
msgstr "Avoiding divisive speech is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.9"
msgid "pharusā vācā, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Harsh speech is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.10"
msgid "pharusāya vācāya veramaṇī dhammo … "
msgstr "Avoiding harsh speech is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.11"
msgid "samphappalāpo, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Talking nonsense is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.12"
msgid "samphappalāpā veramaṇī dhammo … "
msgstr "Avoiding talking nonsense is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.13"
msgid "abhijjhā, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Covetousness is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.14"
msgid "anabhijjhā dhammo … "
msgstr "Contentment is a good principle. … "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.15"
msgid "byāpādo, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Ill will is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:3.16"
msgid "abyāpādo dhammo …. "
msgstr "Good will is a good principle. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.173:4.1"
msgid "Micchādiṭṭhi, bhikkhave, adhammo; "
msgstr "Wrong view is a bad principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:4.2"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi dhammo; "
msgstr "Right view is a good principle. "

msgctxt "an10.173:4.3"
msgid "ye ca micchādiṭṭhipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti, ayaṃ anattho; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by wrong view are bad results. "

msgctxt "an10.173:4.4"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, ayaṃ attho. "
msgstr "And the many skillful qualities fully developed because of right view are good results. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.173:5.1"
msgid "‘Adhammo ca, bhikkhave, veditabbo dhammo ca; "
msgstr "‘You should know bad principles and good principles. "

msgctxt "an10.173:5.2"
msgid "anattho ca veditabbo attho ca. "
msgstr "And you should know bad results and good results. "

msgctxt "an10.173:5.3"
msgid "Adhammañca viditvā dhammañca, anatthañca viditvā atthañca yathā dhammo yathā attho tathā paṭipajjitabban’ti, "
msgstr "Knowing these things, your practice should follow the good principles with good results.’ "

msgctxt "an10.173:5.4"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ, idametaṃ paṭicca vuttan”ti. "
msgstr "That’s what I said, and this is why I said it.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.173:5.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
